query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(a1 b q1 s t1 tq1 u1) */ select acc.location,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.favorite_count >= 0 AND q1.favorite_count <= 10000
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('12.10',
'complex-geometry',
'differential-forms',
'firefox',
'fractions',
'keyboard',
'markov-chains',
'math-history',
'order-theory',
'problem-solving',
'proof-explanation',
'quadratics',
'radicals',
'updates',
'virtualbox')
inner join answer AS a1
on q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_id = a1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('askubuntu',
'math')
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.name IN ('Critic',
'Famous Question',
'Nice Answer',
'Popular Question',
'Revival',
'Scholar',
'Student',
'Supporter')
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND u1.downvotes >= 0 AND u1.downvotes <= 1
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id group by acc.location order by count(*) desc LIMIT 100;
